<mjml>
    <mj-head>
        <mj-include path="../common-head.mjml" />
    </mj-head>
    <mj-body background-color="black">
        <mj-include path="../header.mjml" />
        <mj-include path="../banner-guest.mjml" />
        <mj-section padding="0">
            <mj-column background-color="white" padding-top="20px">
                <mj-text mj-class="heading">
                    Friends are the BEST!
                </mj-text>
                <mj-text>
                    {{booked_on_behalf_of_user_full_name}} has added you to the waitlist for a StarCycle class. Here are the details:
                </mj-text>
                <mj-text>
                    <ul style="text-align:left">
                        <li style="padding-bottom: 1em;">
                            You're on the waitlist to ride at {{class_time}} on {{class_day_of_week}}, {{class_month}} {{class_date}} {{class_year}}.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Youâ€™ll be riding with {{class_instructors}} at our {{ class_location }} location!
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </mj-text>
                <mj-text>
                    <b>Any questions?</b> Let us know at <a href="mailto:{{contact_email}}">{{contact_email}}</a>. We will send you an email if you get added to class, so keep your eyes peeled! Can't wait to ride with you!
                </mj-text>
                <mj-text>
                    <b>{{class_site_name}}</b><br>
                    {{class_location_address}}
                </mj-text>
                <mj-include path="../contact-signature.mjml" />
                <mj-text padding="50px" padding-top="15px">
                    <b>Don't have a StarCycle account?</b>  You can create one here: <a href="https://www.starcycleride.com/">https://www.starcycleride.com/</a>
                </mj-text>
            </mj-column>
        </mj-section>
        <mj-include path="../footer.mjml" />
    </mj-body>
</mjml>